name: Shree Women Multi Coloured Kurta
description:
Style Note
shree kurta for the authentic Desi vibe. Get your summer prints right with this lovely printed piece. Pair it with airy patialas to nail that Punjabi look, or style it with stretchy leggings for all day comfort. We recommend pairing this simply styled kurta with a blingy pair of leggings or chudidhar for a grand occasion. An ethnic pair of chandelier earrings and you're set to go.

Product Details
Multicoloured round neck kurta, has a mock buttoned placket, three quarter sleeves and side slits

Material and Care
Blended fabric
Hand wash cold
Do not bleach
Hang or line dry

Size and Fit
Regular Fit
